summary: What I’ve realized when I was watching the show is 1) how much I’m so attracted to women more than men (even tho I’m married to...
body: What I’ve realized when I was watching the show is 1) how much I’m so attracted to women more than men (even tho I’m married to a man) and 2) how much I’m struggling to figure out if I wouldn’t mind being with an older woman or a younger one. The struggle IS real.

summary: Can you recommend any shows that are similar in tone and vibe to Killing Eve? I can’t get enough of the show but want to find...
question: Can you recommend any shows that are similar in tone and vibe to Killing Eve? I can’t get enough of the show but want to find something else like it.
answer:
Oooh, good question. The vibe and tone are pretty unique to KE but here are some shows I’ve seen it compared to:

Barry, Castle Rock, Counterpart, D.E.B.S (movie), Doctor Foster, Elementary, The Fall, Fleabag, Hannibal, Luther, Person of Interest, Sharp Objects. 

I’ve only seen half of these and imdb recommended a couple of them so please add any shows I’ve not mentioned in the replies. (edited)
